<div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card ">
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <hr>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag "IMG_0112.jpg", width: 250, alt: "profile image"%>

          <div class="skills">
            <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
              <div class="skill">
                <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div
                    class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                    role="progressbar"
                    aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                    aria-valuemax="100"
                    style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  ></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-8">
          <p class="card-text">I'm still a kid. Put a fishing rod (fly rod) in my hand and it is a good day.</p>

          <p class="card-text">My experience with programming goes back many years in several different industries.
            I completed the Bloc bootcamp while working full time. Often working late into the evening until tasks
            were completed. Work Harder. Be Smarter.  Software is a live industry, during my downtime I have been
            exploring new libraries and new languages ( React and ES6). I bring experiences from management to
            customer service to the software developer niche. My name is Keith Robinson, and I am a  Software Developer.
            I bring a strong work ethic,  professional appearance, and willingness to learn.</p>
          <p>
           <button
             class="btn btn-primary"
             type="button"
             data-toggle="collapse"
             data-target="#jobHistory"
             aria-expanded="false"
             aria-controler="jobHistory"
           >
             Job History
           </button>

           <button
             class="btn btn-primary"
             type="button"
             data-toggle="collapse"
             data-target="#education"
             aria-expanded="false"
             aria-controler="education"
           >
             Education
           </button>
         </p>

         <p>
           <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
             <div class="card card-block">
               Wynn Las Vegas<br/> 3131 Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV <br/>
               Golf Professional (Caddie)<br/>
               April 2005 to December 2017
             </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              Cascata Golf Course<br/> 1 Cascata Drive,<br/>
              Boulder City, NV 89005 <br/>
              Golf Professional (Caddie)<br/>
               September 2002 to April 2005
             </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              Top Tool Company<br/>
              3100 84th Lane NE, Minneapolis, MN 55449 <br/>
              Program  Manager / Estimator <br/> 2002
             </div>
           </div>

           <div class="collapse" id="education">
             <div class="card card-block">
               Bloc.io
             </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
               Boston University
             </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
               University of Minnesota
             </div>
           </div>
         </p>
       </div>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
